narratives.question_text: How would you summarize ECON 111 01 for a fellow student? Would you recommend ECON 111 01 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: Great class and recommend people to take!

If you want to learn basic Spanish in 3 months, you should take this course. The course definitely prepares you more for reading/writing than it does for listening/speaking, but this is to be expected because the latter are much harder to get accustomed to.
I would definitely recommend this class to a fellow student who was interested in learning Spanish for the first time. I would describe this class as being a rigorous introductory course.
Essentially learning vocabulary and grammar The class follows the book pretty closely, making it easy to study for the class.
